      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything is just so quiet now. i walk into the kitchen and i forget for a second that he isn't there, and then it hits me all over again. the house feels like an empty shell. i dont even know why i bother getting out of bed anymore. it feels like i'm just walking through a life that doesn't belong to me anymore.",
